独立后，凯莎“来改变世界”：“当你处于恐惧状态时，你无法创造” https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-is-coming-to-change-the-world-after-going-independent-when-youre-in-a-state-of-fear-you-无法创建-3775704？utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=kesha-即将独立后改变世界，当你处于恐惧状态时，你不能-创造Alex RigottiWed, 17 Jul 2024 10:38:03 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3775704 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kesha-Singer-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Kesha（摄影：Lisa Lake/Getty Images for Welcome America, Inc.）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kesha-Singer-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kesha-Singer-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kesha-Singer-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kesha-Singer-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kesha-Singer-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kesha-Singer-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “人类在宇宙中永远失去录制声音的权利，这太疯狂了”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-is-coming-to-change-the-world-after-going-independent-when-youre-in-a-state-of-fear-you-cannot-create-3775704">凯莎独立后“即将改变世界”的帖子：“当你处于恐惧状态时，你无法创造”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kesha-Singer-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Kesha（摄影：Lisa Lake/Getty Images for Welcome America, Inc.）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kesha-Singer-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kesha-Singer-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kesha-Singer-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kesha-Singer-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kesha-Singer-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kesha-Singer-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kesha">凯莎</a>表示，在最终成为一名独立艺术家后，她将“来改变世界”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/kesha-gag-order-rick-rubin-tik-tok-3445064">凯莎谈狂野的新专辑《Gag Order》：“当我感到被看到、听到和接受时，我很高兴”</a></li></ul><p>这位歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-is-now-reportedly-finally-free-from-dr-lukes-kemosabe-record-label-3560956">去年 12 月宣布离开 RCA 和 Kemosabe Records，</a>随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-kesha-debut-independent-song-joyride-3771070">于 7 月 4 日分享了她作为独立艺术家的第一首单曲“Joyride”</a> 。</p><p>现在，凯莎向<em><a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/jeffconway/2024/07/16/kesha-talks-new-music-and-achieving-her-independence-i-am-coming-to-change-the-world/">《福布斯》</a></em>公开了自己不受合同约束的事情，她告诉该刊物：“一个人在宇宙中永远失去录制声音的权利，这太疯狂了。”她接着说，“我正在考虑改变围绕这一问题的诉讼”，并补充说，这是“艺术创作行业的残酷行为”。</p><p>凯莎还宣布了她的新厂牌凯莎唱片，并表示她“非常高兴能够为艺术家建立一个安全的空间，因为创造和恐惧不能共存。” “当你处于恐惧状态时，你无法创造，我从个人经验中知道这一点，”她补充道。</p><p>这位歌手开玩笑说，在建立传统唱片公司模式的同时，Kesha 还在寻找“有创造力、突破界限、创新的技术创造者，他们想要改变音乐行业的运作方式，并为整个行业带来新的透明度。”</p><p> “我创办了自己的唱片公司，我要改变世界，亲爱的，”她后来在采访中说道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3566023" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3566023" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3566023" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kesha-2023-getty.jpg" alt="克莎" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kesha-2023-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kesha-2023-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kesha-2023-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kesha-2023-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kesha-2023-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/kesha-2023-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3566023" class="wp-caption-text">克莎。图片来源：Jamie McCarthy/Getty Images for Christian Siriano。</figcaption></figure><p>在与 Kemosabe Records 创始人 Luke 博士进行了漫长的法律斗争后，Kesha 与 Kemosabe Records 分道扬镳。这位出生于洛杉矶的歌手最初于 2014 年起诉卢克博士，声称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/keha-5-1239397">他对她进行了性侵犯和情感虐待。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-legal-team-court-hear-singer-appeals-before-dr-luke-trial-3300963">他否认了这些指控</a>，并对凯莎提出反诉，声称她违反了与他的唱片合同，并捏造指控，试图摆脱交易。凯莎维持了她最初对卢克博士的指控。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-is-now-reportedly-finally-free-from-dr-lukes-kemosabe-record-label-3560956">两人在该案定于 2023 年 6 月开庭审理的一个月前就诽谤诉讼达成和解</a>。</p><p>凯莎今年一直在预告新音乐，首先是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-teases-new-music-on-cardboard-sign-in-a-los-angeles-car-park-3565977">在洛杉矶用纸板牌宣布这一消息</a>。此后，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-plays-her-first-show-as-a-free-motherfucking-woman-at-weho-pride-3762649">在 WeHo Pride 上以“他妈的自由女人”的身份首次表演</a>，她告诉观众：“今晚还有其他人感到他妈的自由吗？”。</p><p>在其他新闻中，女演员阿比盖尔·布莱斯琳似乎<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/abigail-breslin-sppears-to-criticise-katy-perry-for-working-with-dr-luke-pledges-support-for-kesha-3774060">批评凯蒂·佩里与卢克博士合作，并承诺支持凯莎。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-is-coming-to-change-the-world-after-going-independent-when-youre-in-a-state-of-fear-you-cannot-create-3775704">凯莎独立后“即将改变世界”的帖子：“当你处于恐惧状态时，你无法创造”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
